description: Contact us at our various offices

accordian.heading: Memphis
accordian.heading-detail: Informa Economics Memphis serves as the base for all the firm's operations.
accordian.body-content-intro: Informa Economics Washington specializes in the analysis of government policies, programs and regulations.
accordian.body-content: It is also home to Informa's Feed Ingredients Group. This business unit provides price  discovery, publications, analysis, consulting and cross-hedging analysis on co-products produced or used in the feed, rendering, cottonseed, grain milling, pet food, biodiesel,  ethanol and oleo chemicals industries.
